G,T: [1,\infty) \to \mathbb R
G(x)=\sum_{n \leq x} T\left(\frac{x}{n}\right)
T(x)=O(x)
T(x) \sim cx (x \to \infty)
G(x) \sim cx\log{x} (x \to \infty)
